      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0643P0-04561'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0643P0_20030127_GCR_38' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Lord Goodhart</span> moved Amendment No. 96:
        <q>Page 19, line 8, at end insert "unless disclosure would be incompatible with a Convention right within the meaning of the <a href="/acts/human-rights-act-1998">Human Rights Act 1998</a> (c. 42)</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0643P0-04562'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0643P0_20030127_GCR_39' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
