        <q>Page 20, line 15, at end insert&#x2014;</q>
        <q>(b) direct a senior customs officer to apply, or arrange for a customs officer to apply, for such an order.</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0643P0-04636'>
