            <q>any person detained in custody",</q>
            as the Scottish provision states? In other words, are the provisions for England and Wales the same as those for Scotland? If so, why does it take so many more words to state the position in England than in Scotland?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0643P0-04743'>
        <a name='S5LV0643P0_20030127_GCR_220'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-bassam' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
