            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_153gc' title='Col. 153GC &mdash; HL Deb 27 January 2003 vol 643 c153GC' name='column_153gc' href='#column_153gc' rel='bookmark'>153GC</a>
            found a different solution. As one is much shorter than the other, I should think that we could use the shorter one for both. I am not making a nationalistic point, of course, but it is quite interesting to see the same thing repeated in quite a different form.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0643P0-04745'>
        <a name='S5LV0643P0_20030127_GCR_222'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-bassam' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
