        Clause 48 [<span class="italic">Transfer of EU etc. prisoner to assist UK investigation</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0643P0-04768'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0643P0_20030127_GCR_245' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
