      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0643P0-04808'>
        <a name='S5LV0643P0_20030127_GCR_285'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-filkin' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0643P0_20030127_GCR_285' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Filkin' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-david-filkin" title="Mr David Filkin">Lord Filkin</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I beg to move Amendment No. 126.
          </p>
