        <q>Page 29, line 44, after "removal" insert "or reduction</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0643P0-04820'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0643P0_20030127_GCR_297' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The noble Baroness said: Since this is one of those very rare occasions&#x2014;like hens' teeth&#x2014;when the Government agree to an Opposition amendment, I am very keen to get this in. I apologise to the Chairman for making heavy weather. I beg to move.
      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_166gc' title='Col. 166GC &mdash; HL Deb 27 January 2003 vol 643 c166GC' name='column_166gc' href='#column_166gc' rel='bookmark'>166GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0643P0-04821'>
